      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The wind slabs remain in some cases prone to triggering. They are lying on a crust. <br/> <br/> Sunshine and high temperatures will give rise as the day progresses to increasing moistening of the snowpack especially on very steep sunny slopes. <br/> <br/> There is more snow than usual. At intermediate altitudes there are 150 to 250 cm of snow, and even more in some localities."
      },
